@prefix ex: <https://vocab.cfaa.eus/broaching/>.
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>.
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>.
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>.
@prefix admin: <https://admin-shell.io/dictionary/>.

owl:Ontology rdfs:comment "Ontología para planos mecánicos y esquemas de fluidos de una máquina de brochado." .

### Clases ###
ex:ConjuntoContrapeso a owl:Class .
ex:PlatoDivisor a owl:Class .
ex:ConjuntoCepillos a owl:Class .
ex:EsquemaHidraulico a owl:Class .
ex:Deposito a owl:Class .
ex:SensorNivel a owl:Class .
ex:Motor a owl:Class, admin:Motor .
ex:Bomba a owl:Class .
ex:Retorno a owl:Class .
ex:Sensor a owl:Class, admin:Sensor .

